Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限的时间将跳动停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们悄声无息地燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界已经脱轨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在无须一切顾虑留情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用神器「佩露索娜」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(允许)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全装备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(完成)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(开战)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,8)}{\bord2\1c&H3535FF&\3c&HCFCFCF&}炎发灼眼的讨伐者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(彻底解决)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…就已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我和阿拉斯拖鲁会解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮他找到完美无缺的火焰之雾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是留下男人而死去的女人最后的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  比鲁海尔米娜 提亚玛特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿你们拥有天下无敌的好运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千征令」奥尔贡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经让炎发灼眼的讨伐者订下契约了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎发灼眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在她习惯这个世界的这期间里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不可以让你逃走是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既非炎发灼眼的讨伐者也非我是也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩…彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「彩虹之翼」梅利希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的誓言 重要的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果手下留情的话可伤脑筋了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我先练练手…的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了呢 千征令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙你关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要测试我「虹天剑」的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比你更适合的人选了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  马上结束它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订下契约时的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这契约并不是什么命运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样我还是要自己选择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要想办法从这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要与强者交手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量正涌出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…这就是火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是赌上生死的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是传说中的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该也有什么弱点的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点就能破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:07:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是「夜笠」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎发灼眼的讨伐者所穿着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我翅膀的一部分化成的黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…以赐予强者武具为使命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我自愿成为密司提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说人类自己成为密司提斯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强者…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…寻求与其相称之强者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…自愿成为密司提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是指那把大太刀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…铠甲武士「天目一个」和大太刀「贽殿遮那」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有制作这些的刀匠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎这三个人格混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:09:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐予超越人类的强者注入我生命精华的武具——贽殿遮那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为寻求与之相称的强者  自愿成为密司提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了寻找那个强者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心甘情愿舍弃作为人的一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和我一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以自己的意志 来寻找自己的归属
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心一意的前进着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将成为你主人的强者…就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到了这会儿 就不必说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比鲁海尔米娜·卡卢梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我只是为了完成与她的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而苟活到现在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么乱来的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真担心刚刚得到的火焰之雾就这么失去了也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常清楚只是偶然成功的罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比锻炼还艰苦一百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比红世之徒还可怕…一千倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然说了  就要负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…看来好像某个家伙被干掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了大规模的崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉是…红世的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 阿拉斯拖鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢的人可以随意处置对方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不像是对所迷上的女人提出的条件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有三条约定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在扰乱世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能的锻炼在我之后出现的炎发灼眼的讨伐者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的决战  虽然很艰苦但尽兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「彩虹之翼」梅利希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想见你啊…炎发灼眼的讨伐者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 火焰之雾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比鲁海尔米娜·卡卢梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想一下我们现在身处此地的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来实现她的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…大概只是为了这个…而在一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个彻彻底底…令人讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正见证着新时代的来临是也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…新的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天目一个的力量就只有大太刀而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个不应使用自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而以格斗去迎战的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我们红世之徒对战时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光从表面的攻击来判断战斗方式是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外表运动的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要感觉内部存在之力的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是察觉自在法的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对外观的警戒也不能放松
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  必须记住的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们红世之徒所操纵的自在法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是会引起任何不可能发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊慌没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意现实存在的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我们的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和红世有关的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该闭嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比鲁海尔米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了新时代的来临是也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们也该告别了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长久以来承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:21:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话至今为止的努力便没有意义了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后任何事都必须一个人去做了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「没问题」这句话就是这意思是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望务必能够谅解是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要照我们所教的去做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便没有问题是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在又和天壤之劫火在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须担心了是也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(没问题)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比鲁海尔米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没我看着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜食也不可以吃得太多…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望紧紧拥抱你是也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那么喜欢吃蜜瓜包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在御崎市出现的调律师卡姆辛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.60,0:24:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于开始行动的「扮装舞会」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后思念着悠二的一位少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.61,0:24:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了真正的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.90,0:24:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  新的序章
